[ProMED-mail thanks Joel Hutcheson for pointing out the error in the EID article cited in the post above. Two other alert readers, Dr Charles Calisher and Jerome Bouquet also reported the error. Interestingly, this error apparently has been corrected in the EID paper, published ahead of print, and now the corrected _Haemaphysalis longicornis_ appears in the paper http://wwwnc.cdc.gov/eid/article/20/6/14-0003_article.htm. - Mod.TY

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2489227,186.]
